47 "§ 90-757. Examinations.
48 (a) Evidence of Examination. – To meet the requirement of examination under this
49 Article for nuclear medicine technology, radiation therapy, radiography, radiologist assistant, or
50 sonography, the Board shall accept current certification and registration by a certification
51 organization recognized by the Board in the applicant's or licensee's modality.
